emble.","year":-1520},{"id":"recv125imJGZCStXF","ref":"Job.9.7","text":"Which commandeth the sun, and it riseth not; and sealeth up the stars.","year":-1520},{"id":"recqICbaazZw8a5N9","ref":"Job.9.8","text":"Which alone spreadeth out the heavens, and treadeth upon the waves of the sea.","year":-1520}]}
